====Case suffix====
#Suffix for the [[abessive]] case, without.

====Synonyms====
*''(without''): [[ilman]], [[vailla]]

====Usage notes====
*Suffixed to the [[genitive]] stem in the singular, to the same stem as the [[inessive]] in the plural.
*Not very commonly used, especially the singular forms.

===Etymology 2===
Derived from the [[assimilate]]d final consonant of the stem, *k or *h, plus the partitive suffix [[-ta]].

====Case suffix====

#A suffix for the [[partitive]] singular.

====Usage notes====
*Used only for words whose nominative singular ends in ''-e'' and which lengthen that final ''-e'' in other singular cases. For declension, see [[Wiktionary:Finnish inflection types#48|Finnish inflection type 48]].

